title: Simple carrot cake
ingredients: ['250g self-raising flour', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '400g caster sugar', '350ml vegetable oil', '4 eggs', '350g grated carrots', '120g chopped walnuts', 'Cream cheese icing', '225g cream cheese', '110g margarine, softened', '450g icing sugar', '120g chopped walnuts', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract']
